snippet.title: HCA - First Annual RVA Birth Community Celebration
snippet.description:
Henrico Doctors’ Hospital held the first annual RVA Birth Community Celebration at the Quirk Hotel on February 6th, 2016. Guests were invited to join Henrico Doctors’ Hospital for an evening of discussion about midwifery and birth choices, including a screening of the document ‘Mama Sherpas’, featuring collaborative midwifery practice in a hospital setting. 

Special featured guests included the Executive Producers of ‘Mama Sherpas’, Abby Epstein and Ricki Lake, and featured speaker, Ginger Breedlove, CNM and President of the American College of Nurse Midwives.
